data.description: Prepare to embark on an exciting journey to your dream home, tucked away at the end of a charming cul-de-sac. This remarkable end-unit residence promises not just a place to live, but a lifestyle that's both convenient and lavish.  As you enter, you'll be greeted by an elegant foyer and soaring 10-foot ceilings that set the stage for a home that's nothing short of beautiful!  But the fun begins when you step outside! Your new expanded patio wraps around the home, offering more outdoor space than most single-family homes. It's like having your very own adventure playground, perfect for everything from picnics to impromptu BBQ. Inside, the party continues with a modern and chic interior featuring dazzling diamond laid tile. The upgraded kitchen with its 42-inch cabinets is a cook's paradise.  Feeling creative? The finished garage is your canvas for crafting a hangout space that's uniquely you! The generously sized bedrooms provide plenty of room for sleepovers and pillow forts, and the second-floor laundry room is like a secret lair for laundry day superheroes.The master suite is a spa-worthy retreat with a soaking tub, dual sink vanity, stall shower, and a private toilet space. Imagine pampering yourself in style! But the most fun spot of all? This home has a second floor wrap-around balcony that's perfect for stargazing, people-watching, or just enjoying the fresh air with your morning coffee.  And don't forget the convenient extras like accordion shutters for peace of mind and top-rated schools just around the corner. Plus, you're just a short 10-minute drive from the beach and a mere 5 minutes from the mall for endless entertainment options. This home is more than just a place to live; it's where the fun never stops. Don't miss your chance to make it yours. Schedule a viewing today and get ready to experience a lifestyle that's both fabulous and full of fun!
